.test-text-to-send
  .title
    Subject
  .massage-body.subject
    &lt;Candidate Name&gt;, #{@company.name} has chosen you to write an Assessment
  .title
    Message
  .massage-body.massage
    %p
      Dear &lt;Candidate Name&gt;,
    %p
      You have been chosen by 
      %b #{@company.name} 
      to complete the Jombay Questionnaire. 
    %p
      Please click on the following link and fill out the Questionnaire. 
    %p
      %b
        URL: &lt;candidate specific url&gt;
    %p
      The Questionnaire results will be used to help #{@company.name} better support your job satisfaction and career development. There are no right or wrong answers. The questionnaire will take approximately 20 minutes to complete.    
    %p
      If you face any difficulty while answering the questionnaire, 
      call Prakhar Srivastava from the Jombay team on 
      %b +91-87960-29607 
      or email
      %a{:href=>"mailto:prakhar@jombay.com", :title=>"For any queries Mail to Prakhar"}
        prakhar@jombay.com.
      %br
    %p
      Best Regards,
      %br/
      - if ["SuperAdmin"].include? current_user.type
        Prakhar Srivastava
        %br
        Jombay
      - else
        = current_user.name  
      %br/
    %p
      P.S.: If the link above does not work, or wraps over 2 or more lines, please copy and paste the link directly into your browser and ensure that there are no spaces in the between.   
